high_descs: Turn left, move forward, turn right, step forward, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the cup on the table.
Turn right, go forward, turn left, move forward, then turn left to face the counter with the coffee maker.
Put the cup on the counter, in front of the coffee maker.
Pick up the spoon in front of the coffee maker.
Put the spoon in the cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a cup on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go just past the white table to your right, then turn to your right, and then right again so that you are facing the loaf of bread on the table.
Pick up the gold wine glass, behind the loaf of bread, on the table.
Turn to your right and go around the table to your left, then walk across the kitchen until you reach the dishwasher with the coffee maker of your left,
Place the wine glass on the dishwasher, in front of the spoon.
Pick up the spoon behind the wine glass, on the dishwasher
Place the spoon in the wine glass.
anns.task_desc: Put  a wine glass containing a spoon, on the dishwasher.

high_descs: move to the left side of the table ahead of you
pick up a cup from the table
move to the counter to the left of the fridge
put the cup on the counter
pick up a spoon from the counter
put the spoon the cup on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cup on a counter with spoon inside.
